data.description: This is a must see beautiful home with a pool (16' X 32'). Gazebo for entertaining. Plantation shutters. Beautiful oversized sunroom with lots of windows and 2 entrance doors, one to the driveway and the other to the backyard. Large metal wired shed for storage/workshop with double doors and a lean to shed on the side. The fireplace in the Great room is woodburning and/or gas, it currently has gas logs in it. Goodman 3.5 ton AC and Heat Pump Air to Air and it is electric. In the laundry room is a tankless gas water heater. Stainless steel Samsung electric flattop stove, Samsung 2 door refrigerator/freezer with ice maker/water on the door. Kitchen & great room both have a pass thru to the bonus room. Large beautiful fenced back yard with drive through gate. All appliances, ceiling fans, mirrors, light fixtures to stay with the home. The movable décor belongs to the seller and/or listing agent and will be taken out prior to closing. Off street parking. Close to lots of shopping/dining.
